---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Fixed Background Image Layer -->
  <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 bg-center bg-cover" style="background-image: url('/assets/roaming-bear-bg.png');"></div>

  <!-- Gradient Overlay Layer -->
  <div class="bg-overlay"></div>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero fade-in-up">
    <h1 class="hero-title text-gradient">
      Welcome to Roaming Bear Honey Co.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      Local. Sustainable. Wild-crafted honey from the forest to your table.
    </p>
    <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-primary">
      Shop Now
    </a>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Content Section -->
  <section class="relative z-30 py-20 px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="container-responsive">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="border-accent pl-4 sm:pl-6 mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
            Our Story
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p>Roaming Bear Honey Co. started with a simple truth: when you slow down enough to truly <em>listen</em> to the hum of a hive, something in you shifts.</p>
            <p>We believe great honey doesn't begin in the jar—it begins in the soil, the weather, the temperament of a queen, and the patience of a keeper.</p>
            <p>Every jar we offer reflects what we've observed, tended, and protected. This isn't a race to scale—it's a commitment to resilience, transparency, and emotional resonance.</p>
            <p>But we're not doing this alone.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p>Through our <strong>Friends of the Bear</strong> initiative, we invite others into the story—via hive adoption, collaborative publishing, and sharing small-batch harvests.</p>
            <p>We showcase their honey. Their practices. Their stories.</p>
            <p>Roaming Bear isn't just about honey. It's about protecting the dignity of small-scale care and giving keepers space to be heard.</p>
            <p>Welcome to Roaming Bear.</p>
            <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]/70 italic pt-2">
              Every jar supports sustainable beekeeping and promotes biodiversity in our ecosystems. Taste the difference in every drop.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;
  }
</style>
